<item>
            <title>[TIKA-3922] Documentation: Tika Config Cors is not a boolean value</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-3922</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Documentation in XML config file is outdated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the tika server config, the &amp;lt;cors&amp;gt; element doesn&apos;t support the option &quot;all&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, the &quot;*&quot; option works to allow all origins.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/tika/blob/2.6.0/tika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/server/core/TikaServerProcess.java#L354&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/tika/blob/2.6.0/tika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/server/core/TikaServerProcess.java#L354&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/tika/blob/2.5.0/tika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/resources/tika-server-config-default.xml#L40&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/tika/blob/2.5.0/tika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/resources/tika-server-config-default.xml#L40&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
